name: Create Kizeo Forms users from new Microsoft 365 worksheet rows
description:
Every time you add a new row to a Microsoft 365 Excel worksheet, Make will automatically create a user in Kizeo Forms.

Your Microsoft 365 Excel worksheet has to contain headers. The template uses this [worksheet](https://1drv.ms/x/s!Au92ZQn17jiNswCtzVT_mC8wVeb9?e=Gnl0lM).
